    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. Discretization error GCI within acceptance threshold. Validation output comparison error within 15% for all QoIs. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the conditions described in this assessment. Note: this package is filed under the Minimal profile; a structured Context of Use object has not been included, and the intended-use scope is described only in the narrative above.",
